a thousand features which we're gonna demo

00:03:44.939 --> 00:03:49.019
in a few minutes that describe and display
how you can use it in the very complicated

00:03:49.019 --> 00:03:54.019
world of multitasking, how we can use all
of the tricks and treatments to make it happen.

00:03:54.019 --> 00:03:58.999
